        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-06 21:27:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nI believe removing the sphinxcontrib-needs templates has broken the build of the enumerated requirements within the VNFRQTS project.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "310eb7fe2a7ae8a001cee64862194166e82eefc2",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3213,
          "name": "Aric Gardner",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "agardner@linuxfoundation.org",
          "username": "agardner"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-06 22:38:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4:\n> \n> I believe removing the sphinxcontrib-needs templates has broken the build of the enumerated requirements within the VNFRQTS project\n\ncan you elaborate?",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "a66a9b43708baa440bc1d5b03eb0446e66369091",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3213,
          "name": "Aric Gardner",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "agardner@linuxfoundation.org",
          "username": "agardner"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-06 22:42:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4:\n> \n> > Patch Set 4:\n> > \n> > I believe removing the sphinxcontrib-needs templates has broken the build of the enumerated requirements within the VNFRQTS project\n> \n> can you elaborate?\n\nAnything that was removed from docs/conf.py that was required will need to be added to https://github.com/lfit/releng-docs-conf/blob/master/docs_conf/defaults/onap.yaml\n\nOr if it is only needed for one project, then that project can customize their conf.py",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "c01b72ccd51c6de5cfe7eeeacc0413bd3cbcae40",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3271,
          "name": "Hagop Bozawglanian",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "hagop.bozawglanian@att.com",
          "username": "hb755d"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-07 18:52:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nYes, for the sphinxcontrib-needs extension to work, there needs to be a template in the conf.py file that signifies the metadata allowed. This was removed to the conf.py file from the Doc project and not added in the onap.yaml file you pointed to. Not sure if other projects use the sphinxcontrib-needs extension but this is necessary for the vnfrqts project.\n\nI commented on the section that is needed in the conf.py file.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "2a08261aaa112bec49452798aa87ec556347b681",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3213,
          "name": "Aric Gardner",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "agardner@linuxfoundation.org",
          "username": "agardner"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-02-07 19:00:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nOkay, thanks addressed in https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/doc/+/101402/",
        "patchset_number": 4
      }
